breeze and Jason was more interested in what
ocean life would be like in the future, so

00:44:54.299 --> 00:45:00.239
he wanted to work with marine, a marine painting
where he would create effects that evoke the

00:45:00.239 --> 00:45:07.010
motion of waves in the sea. Prior work and
inspiration, I know for me, personally, I

00:45:07.010 --> 00:45:14.349
really like Jacco Oliviers work. He does really
large animated paintings which he then projects

00:45:14.349 --> 00:45:23.319
onto a wall and The Sperm Whale is a collective
