01:02:34.969 --> 01:02:38.910
and I, it was up, I was there for a week in
residence and so I spoke to a lot of different

01:02:38.910 --> 01:02:45.569
kinds of people. And disturbingly, the response
was how comforting this piece was to them

01:02:45.569 --> 01:02:53.049
because they felt like, look at your eyes,
they felt like this piece demonstrated our

01:02:53.049 --> 01:02:58.729
adaptability and that in the end, we would
all be ok.

